Record Class Curse

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Record
fr.uge.backpackhero.item.Curse
All Implemented Interfaces:
Item
public record Curse(List<Position> pos) extends Record implements Item
Represents a curse item. A curse usually occupies space in the backpack but provides no benefit and cannot be meaningfully used in combat.
